+### Demo tools (`src/components/demo/`)
+
+4 Claude-powered tools on `/demo` with a shared `ChatInterface` component. Each chat API route uses a `createChatHandler` factory from `src/lib/chat-handler.ts` — routes are ~5 lines each, all shared logic (streaming, error handling, analytics) lives in the factory.
