+# TODOS
+
+## Deferred from v2 (CEO Review 2026-03-18)
+
+### Conversation Persistence
+**What:** Save chat history to localStorage so visitors can return and continue.
+**Why:** A hiring manager who tries the Plant Diagnostic on their phone might want to revisit on desktop.
+**Effort:** S (CC: ~15 min)
+**Priority:** P2
+**Depends on:** Core tools working
+
+### Anthropic Employee Easter Egg
+**What:** If someone mentions working at Anthropic, shift to an insider-aware response acknowledging they're evaluating a candidate.
+**Why:** Small delight moment for the exact audience that matters most.
+**Effort:** S (CC: ~10 min — system prompt addition)
+**Priority:** P3
+**Depends on:** Core tools working
+
+### Dynamic OG Images for /demo
+**What:** Generate OG images for the /demo page that reflect what was discussed (e.g., "Claude Assessment for Refining Operations").
+**Why:** When someone shares the demo link on LinkedIn, the preview would be personalized.
+**Effort:** M (CC: ~30 min — Satori/OG image generation)
+**Priority:** P3
+**Depends on:** Shareable briefing working
+
+### Response References
+**What:** Claude's responses cite specific sections of the thesis, with links back to /thesis#section.
+**Why:** Connects the demo tools to the strategic depth of the thesis. Shows integrated thinking.
+**Effort:** S (CC: ~20 min — system prompt + link rendering)
+**Priority:** P2
+**Depends on:** /thesis page with anchor IDs
+
+### Personal Site Integration
+**What:** Embed the Anthropic pitch as an unlisted page within chrispratt.com, allowing visitors to navigate to the broader personal portfolio.
+**Why:** Creates a complete picture — the Anthropic pitch is one piece of a larger professional story.
+**Effort:** M (CC: ~1 hour — depends on personal site architecture)
+**Priority:** P1 (after v2 ships)
+**Depends on:** Personal site project being ready
